// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1745 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 542a64b0-35f6-521e-953b-8484b0804376

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
